plot: Rabbits have overrun the gated Orange County community, and Jeana's son Shane has gained the reputation as the official 'rabbit hunter'. Kimberly is feeling neighborhood pressure to upgrade her car, meanwhile, Jo's fiance Slade plans a high-powered business meeting with a potential client. Vicki takes Briana and a group of cheerleaders on a cruise, where Vicki's wild side emerges and Lauri's troubles continue to mount and her son, Josh, gets into big trouble at school and gets arrested—Anonymous
